stars: INSERT INTO devdata.stars (id, owner, repo, starred_by, starred_at, _cursor) VALUES(%s, %s, %s,%s,%s,%s) ON CONFLICT (id) DO NOTHING
forks: INSERT INTO devdata.forks (id, owner, repo, created_by, created_at, _cursor) VALUES(%s, %s, %s,%s,%s,%s) ON CONFLICT (id) DO NOTHING
issues: INSERT INTO devdata.issues(id, owner, repo, created_by, created_at, status, closed_by, closed_at, _cursor) VALUES(%s, %s, %s, %s, %s, %s, %s, %s, %s) ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE SET (status, closed_by, closed_at) = (EXCLUDED.status, EXCLUDED.closed_by, EXCLUDED.closed_at)
pullrequests: INSERT INTO devdata.pullrequests(id, owner, repo, created_by, created_at, status, merged_by, merged_at, _cursor) VALUES(%s,%s,%s,%s,%s,%s,%s,%s,%s) ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE SET (status, merged_by, merged_at) = (EXCLUDED.status, EXCLUDED.merged_by, EXCLUDED.merged_at)
agstats: INSERT INTO devdata.agstats (repo, owner, _at,  stars, forks, open_issues, closed_issues, total_issues , open_pull_requests, merged_pull_requests) VALUES(%s, %s, %s, %s, %s, %s, %s, %s, %s, %s) ON CONFLICT (repo) DO UPDATE SET (_at, stars, forks, open_issues, closed_issues, total_issues, open_pull_requests, merged_pull_requests) = (EXCLUDED._at, EXCLUDED.stars, EXCLUDED.forks, EXCLUDED.open_issues, EXCLUDED.closed_issues, EXCLUDED.total_issues, EXCLUDED.open_pull_requests, EXCLUDED.merged_pull_requests)
orgstats: INSERT INTO devdata.orgstats (owner, coin_name, coin_symbol, _at, repo_count) VALUES(%s, %s, %s, %s, %s) ON CONFLICT (owner) DO UPDATE SET (_at, repo_count) = (EXCLUDED._at, EXCLUDED.repo_count)
commits: INSERT INTO devdata.commits (id, owner, repo, committed_by, committed_at) VALUES(%s, %s, %s, %s, %s) ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE SET (committed_by, committed_at) = (EXCLUDED.committed_by, EXCLUDED.committed_at)
